  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Account Executive (Client Services)",
  "description": "<p>Are you a go-getter? BookMyShow SEA is a regional ticketing start up, and we are looking for big personalities to handle our projects, big or small! We work closely with event promoters and venue owners, and we empower them by providing them with the right tools to successfully manage their end-to-end ticketing journey. Our team is a multi-disciplinary, tight-knit, meticulous, hardworking, and talented bunch. We work closely together to ensure the success of every event, concert, theatre performance, outdoor festival, and major sporting event that we ticket for.</p><p><br /></p><p>Do you have what it takes to:</p><p>· Step up and be the main liaison officer with our numerous promoters?</p><p>· Do what needs to be done to ensure the success of every event?</p><p>· Collaborate with business teams to better understand clients' needs and wants, and to separate what is really needed, vs. what is really wanted?</p><p><br /></p><p>We’re looking for someone who has:</p><p>· A go-getter attitude who never turns down a challenge</p><p>· Passion for creative problem-solving, and who can think out of the box</p><p>· Effective crisis and time management skills</p><p>· Strong written and communication skills</p><p>· A passion for the Arts & Entertainment world (added advantage)</p><p><br /></p><p>This role would be a good fit if you have:</p><p>· A Level, Diploma or Degree in any related field, or equivalent practical experience</p><p>· Will be required to present during events day (Sat, Sun or Public Holiday)</p><p>· No experience or Fresh graduate are welcome to apply</p><p>· Worked in a start-up (added advantage)</p><p><br /></p>",
